These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, february, november
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, baking, sudoku, camping
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, photographer, teacher
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, bellflower, sunflower
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, bird, cat
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who growsiris##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the person who growsiris is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the doctor##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 9. the owner of the cat is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
11. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
13. the teacher is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
14. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
15. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
16. the photographer is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Birthday    | november | december     | february     | april |
| Hobby        | baking  | fishing | sudoku      | camping      |
| Job         | teacher  | doctor    | photographer | coach       |
| Flower       | tulip | iris   | bellflower      | sunflower  |
| Pet   | hamster      | guinea-pig  | bird   | cat      |

