.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, snooker, domino
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, april, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, manager, police-officer
City: marseilles, venice, paris, nizza
There 4 different types of food: peas, pear, pepper, eggplant
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
 3. the police-officer is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
 4. the designer is between the firefighter and the manager##2
 5. the designer is not the person eating pepper##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 9. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
10. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
11. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person eating peas##1
12. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
13. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
14. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing domino##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
16. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
17. the person who's birthday is in february is the person playing canasta##1
18. the person playing canasta is not the firefighter##6
19. the person playing chess is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
20. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
21. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4        |
