The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, photography, singing, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, frog, hedgehog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, martial-arts, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, jazz, reggae, country
 1. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
 2. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 4. the person eating pear is not to the left of the owner of the lizard##8
 5. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of country##1
 7. the fan of reggae is not the person watching western movies##6
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
 9. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
10. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
11. the fan of disco is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
14. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
15. the fan of jazz is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
16. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
17. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
18. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
19. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |    4    |
